# Production on Vercel (this repo): use the API service prefix (see root vercel.json), e.g.:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=/server
#
# Vercel often injects NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL when the backend service is named `api`.
# Leave unset locally unless you proxy to a remote API.
#
# Multi-vehicle rollout flags for the search UI. Keep this in sync with backend ENABLED_VEHICLE_CATEGORIES.
# Example phased rollout: `car,motorcycle` first, then `car,motorcycle,boat`.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLED_VEHICLE_CATEGORIES=car
